    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――BIG4チャレンジよりしばらく前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days ago before the BIG4 Challenge",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2531521857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 12.0333335459
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 12.1666668792
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……ふぅ\nこれくらいで休憩にしようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant‚ pant… Whew.\nLet's take a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.8999994497,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7233.334096299998,
          "startTime": 26.5000002126
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10656.666666699997,
          "startTime": 29.923332783
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3666654806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "渚？　どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa? What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5333352625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "今、ニュースの通知があって。「どりきゅん\n復帰後初のライブバトルで圧倒的勝利」……だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just got a news notification. \"DoriKyun Wins Overwhelmingly\nin First Live Battle Since Comeback\"… That's what it says.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2333341817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……ブランクは全くないって訳ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So there's no blank period at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3666685958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "このスコア……ブランクどころか、活動休止を経て\nさらにパワーアップをしているのでは……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With this score… It's not just that there's no blank period‚ but it seems like\nthey've powered up even more after their hiatus…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0333335459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "……大丈夫、私達なら勝てるよ！　そうでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's okay‚ we can win! Right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9694808383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 58.9333335459
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。そもそもここで揺さぶられていては\nBIG4チャレンジ本番で力を発揮出来ませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. If we're shaken here‚\nwe won't be able to show our full potential at the actual BIG4 Challenge.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7361483316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "そーそー！　楽しんだもん勝ちだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! Whoever has the most fun wins!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2028141717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そう……よね。焦らず、本番までに\nじっくりパフォーマンスを練り上げよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's… right. Let's not rush and carefully refine our performance\nby the actual event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4666668792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわ。そして本番で華麗なる\n勝利を飾ってみせますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. And we'll decorate the stage with\nour glorious victory!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1333335459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "よーし！　さっそく練習再開だー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright! Let's get back to practice!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7460808972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "へ！？　あ～……ま、まぁ？　私はもちろん\nすぐにでも練習を再開して構いませんけれど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? Ah… W-Well?\nI can resume practice right away‚ of course…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.9000002126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、もう少し休憩してもいいんじゃない？\n体が固まらないように注意だけしておこう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ why don’t we take a little more break?\nJust be careful not to stiffen up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5520436823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "（本番まで時間はあまりないけど……）\n（やれることをやるしかない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(There's not much time left until the actual event…)\n(All I can do is do what I can do.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.618710349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.5520436823
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
