      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 111.7775171041
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ good work today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4853843271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。……今回の件\n協力してもらえるのは本当にありがたいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. …For this matter‚\nI'm really grateful for your cooperation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7334721943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.887705777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ、お気になさらず！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No problem at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.887705777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんの情報を私達で集めて\n月ストのサポートをする……燃えますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll gather information on DoriKyun and\nsupport Moon Tempest… It’s exciting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.1422757275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.1138733285
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "橋本さんも他の仕事があるのに\n手伝ってくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for helping me even though\nyou have other work‚ Hashimoto-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.257463048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "……今の月ストは、確実にI-UNITYの時よりも\n成長してると思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I think the current Moon Tempest has definitely grown stronger than\nthey were during I-UNITY.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.3000002126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.3518096981
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-stm005.m4a",
      "text": "ですが……私は休止前のどりきゅんを一度だけ生で\n見たことがあって。あの時の衝撃が忘れられないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However… I saw DoriKyun live once before their break‚\nand I can't forget the shock I felt then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_01-stm006.m4a",
      "text": "そこから休止を経て\nさらにパワーアップしたとなると……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After they’ve taken a hiatus and\nbecome even more powerful…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.6666668792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.9179721572
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
